				<wikidot:authorName>Genshed</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2643500</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I am irresistibly drawn to recall an incident at the San Diego Zoo on a determinate date. I was viewing a display of tortoises when a gaggle of Bright Young Things (presumably SDZ volunteers) scampered past. One exclaimed, 'I didn't know we had turtles!'</p> <p>The distinction between turtles and tortoises was explained, to no apparent purpose.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
